@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 治理 R1-B1：列出邀请
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/member-invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 治理 R1-B1：创建邀请
# @name createInvitation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/member-invitations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newcomer@example.com",
  "organizationId": "1",
  "roleCode": "member",
  "expiresInDays": 7
}

###
@invitationToken = {{createInvitation.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 治理 R1-B1：撤销邀请
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/member-invitations/{{createInvitation.response.body.$.data.id}}/revoke
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 治理 R1-B1：接受邀请（匿名）；
###   - userId 为空且邮箱无对应账号 → 自动创建 pending-activation 用户并返回 setPasswordToken
###   - 已存在用户或显式 userId → 仅加入组织，setPasswordToken=null
# @name acceptInvitation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/member-invitations/accept
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{invitationToken}}",
  "userId": null
}

###
@setPasswordToken = {{acceptInvitation.response.body.$.data.setPasswordToken}}

### 治理 R1-B1：使用一次性 token 设置密码并激活账号（匿名）；token 24h 过期且消费即失效
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/member-invitations/set-password
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "{{setPasswordToken}}",
  "newPassword": "Aa1!Strong#PassChange"
}
